name: TurboTax Canada 2010 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .TT10 files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: TT10 files contain federal tax forms as well as provincial forms for an individual Canadian province. Data can be entered using the TurboTax's EasyStep method or input directly into the forms. The program's Form Lookup feature allows you to view and edit any form individually.
NOTE: Intuit Canada TurboTax was formerly named "QuickTax." Intuit QuickTax 2009 saved tax return files with a .Q09 extension.
